Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.70,0:00:33.41,Default,Hugo,0000,0000,0000,,Angelica, is that it for the orders?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.41,0:00:34.55,Default,Angelica,0000,0000,0000,,Hugo.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.55,0:00:37.80,Default,Angelica,0000,0000,0000,,Assuming his letter is accurate, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.90,0:00:42.40,Default,Hugo,0000,0000,0000,,This is all is for his disciple?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.40,0:00:43.38,Default,Angelica,0000,0000,0000,,Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.55,0:00:46.43,Default,Angelica,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you could call it an \Nintroductory materials kit.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.61,0:00:50.48,Default,Hugo,0000,0000,0000,,Really, though, a disciple? \NFor that half-baked guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.76,0:00:53.05,Default,Angelica,0000,0000,0000,,Hugo.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.91,0:00:56.28,Default,Angelica,0000,0000,0000,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.32,0:00:59.73,Default,Angelica,0000,0000,0000,,All right, let's start.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.73,0:01:00.53,Default,Hugo,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.51,0:01:04.56,Default,Hugo,0000,0000,0000,,Ready when you are, Angelica.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.56,0:01:05.24,Default,Angelica,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.92,0:01:14.58,Default,Angelica,0000,0000,0000,,Dig deeper, dig deeper, droplet.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.93,0:01:17.25,Default,Angelica,0000,0000,0000,,Forge, forge, steel.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.49,0:01:21.94,Default,Angelica,0000,0000,0000,,Part the gold, cut the mortar, turn with...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.42,0:01:31.56,Default,Hugo,0000,0000,0000,,Angelica!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.56,0:01:33.24,Default,Hugo,0000,0000,0000,,What was {\i1}that{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.24,0:01:34.96,Default,Angelica,0000,0000,0000,,It should be around here...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.32,0:01:36.13,Default,Angelica,0000,0000,0000,,Found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.40,0:01:41.69,Default,Angelica,0000,0000,0000,,This is my gift.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.90,0:01:44.13,Default,Angelica,0000,0000,0000,,I hope they like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.18,0:01:50.07,Default,Hugo,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I asked you if \Nthat was all for the orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.42,0:01:52.25,Default,Angelica,0000,0000,0000,,I'd forgotten about this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.49,0:01:54.20,Default,Hugo,0000,0000,0000,,A book from the land of disciples?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.20,0:01:56.30,Default,Angelica,0000,0000,0000,,I found it at the used book store.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.37,0:01:58.60,Default,Angelica,0000,0000,0000,,All right, Hugo.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.60,0:01:59.35,Default,Hugo,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.33,0:02:03.88,Default,Hugo,0000,0000,0000,,Dig deeper, dig deeper, droplet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.70,0:02:07.25,Default,Hugo,0000,0000,0000,,Forge, forge, steel.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.08,0:02:11.64,Default,Hugo,0000,0000,0000,,Part the gold, cut the mortar,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.82,0:02:16.51,Default,Hugo,0000,0000,0000,,turn with those hands the \Nwater wheel of the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.06,0:02:22.99,Default,Hugo,0000,0000,0000,,Let what must go \Nflow to where it must be.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.37,0:02:48.46,Default,Angelica,0000,0000,0000,,Now, take that to Ainsworth \Nand his disciple, Chise, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.87,0:03:29.60,Magus-Episode_Title,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1500,1)}Those Awaiting a Star \N{\fs20}Part 1
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.44,0:04:13.97,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,Morning, Ruth.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.97,0:04:15.59,Default,Ruth,0000,0000,0000,,Morning, Chise.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.83,0:04:43.66,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.66,0:04:46.13,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Is the medicine I requested ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.22,0:04:47.75,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,The cough medicine, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.72,0:05:00.09,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,Elias.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.22,0:05:16.76,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like Darjeeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.93,0:05:17.74,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.83,0:05:18.73,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.00,0:05:22.51,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,We're having a lot of \Ntomato dishes as of late.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.01,0:05:26.60,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,We've got a lot of tomatoes,\Nsince it's summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.93,0:05:28.13,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.12,0:05:45.80,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,Ruth, you're having breakfast, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.74,0:05:51.18,Default,Ruth,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, Chise.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.58,0:05:52.80,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,A gremlin?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.89,0:05:58.74,Default,Ruth,0000,0000,0000,,I was making him fix something he messed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.86,0:06:12.00,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,Time to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.85,0:06:18.89,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,Are you not eating?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.38,0:06:20.83,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's not that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.71,0:06:25.98,Magus-internal/narrator,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,Seems like he's in a bad mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.16,0:06:31.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'll start eating.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.49,0:06:38.30,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,You're spilling it, Ruth.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.29,0:06:41.18,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,Chise.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.34,0:06:42.12,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.49,0:06:43.94,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,What are your plans for today?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.64,0:06:49.66,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be checking on the field in the\N back, to pick whatever is ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.94,0:06:54.65,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,The herbs are maturing, too,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.65,0:06:57.51,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,so I'm thinking of drying all of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.35,0:07:06.60,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,Once I'm done with my morning tasks, \NI'll be studying magic as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.40,0:07:09.70,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,What will you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.35,0:07:13.71,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,There's a book I haven't finished, \Nso I'll read the rest of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.71,0:07:16.27,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,Is it the one I gave you the other day?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.63,0:07:17.52,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.44,0:07:27.96,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,Chise, acquiring knowledge is fine,\N but you need experience as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.03,0:07:32.32,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,It seems kind of dangerous, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.84,0:07:36.50,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I should learn it well first.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.92,0:07:39.05,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,That's important, too,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.67,0:07:43.36,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,but I'm your teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.98,0:07:48.65,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,You can ask me if you ever\N want to experiment.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.65,0:07:50.31,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.17,0:07:57.79,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,I'll pick out a book suitable for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.79,0:07:59.27,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,Let me know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.15,0:08:03.95,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,Coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.66,0:08:20.58,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.68,0:08:22.84,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,All this stuff came crashing down on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.84,0:08:24.01,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.86,0:08:26.22,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,That's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.31,0:08:32.40,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,Angie really stuffed it full, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.89,0:08:34.29,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,Angelica-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.77,0:08:39.15,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,I ordered some learning materials for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.25,0:08:42.33,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,This is all for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.78,0:08:43.60,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.37,0:08:47.88,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,The books are still too advanced for you,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.25,0:08:51.67,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,but I'll make sure you can \Nuse the tools right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.63,0:08:54.67,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.41,0:08:56.29,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.87,0:08:57.58,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.68,0:09:00.57,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,Use this when you go into the forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.21,0:09:03.80,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,Use this when you're gathering fairies.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.03,0:09:06.32,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,This book's very easy to read.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.70,0:09:08.10,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,This one's...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.03,0:09:13.02,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Chise, let's bring this to the study.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.59,0:09:15.59,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,The study?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.10,0:09:19.06,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, have I not told you yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.25,0:09:20.09,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.19,0:09:26.10,Default,Silky,0000,0000,0000,,Stare...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.41,0:09:27.26,Magus-overlap,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,May I finish breakfast first?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.43,0:09:28.64,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,Good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.12,0:09:43.29,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you going in?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.21,0:09:45.26,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.79,0:10:11.88,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.27,0:10:14.62,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,Elias, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.32,0:10:20.29,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,May I tidy up this room?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.82,0:10:28.60,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,I have a feeling it'll be difficult \Nto find things in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.08,0:10:31.55,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I suppose I don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.85,0:10:32.77,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,Ruth.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.90,0:10:33.79,Default,Ruth,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.00,0:10:53.24,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,I never even thought of \Ncleaning the bookshelves.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.74,0:10:59.43,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I sort them, they tend to \Nend up elsewhere on their own.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.51,0:11:09.68,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,Eventually I got sick of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.15,0:11:14.24,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,I told Silky that she doesn't \Nneed to bother, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.54,0:11:19.69,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,B-But, maybe with enough diligence, \Nwe can maintain some order.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.81,0:11:24.33,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,If you think so, it must be true.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.01,0:11:29.03,Default,Ruth,0000,0000,0000,,Chise, why don't we go for a walk?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.73,0:11:50.73,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.67,0:11:54.47,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.78,0:11:56.83,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,for all the new learning materials.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.15,0:11:59.75,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,I'm your magic teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.01,0:12:01.61,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just doing what anyone would.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.86,0:12:07.82,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,I know, but why so many?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.81,0:12:12.28,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,I simply thought you'd need it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.04,0:12:19.71,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing. Never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.80,0:12:26.05,sign_17810_129_Voice_of_the_Lon,Text,0000,0000,0000,,The Lonely Little Star
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.02,0:12:35.88,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,This book...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.76,0:12:38.78,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.24,0:12:41.73,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,Angelica-san sent this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.89,0:12:43.15,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,A gift?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.49,0:12:44.96,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,A Japanese book.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.18,0:12:46.35,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,How unusual.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.99,0:12:48.77,Default,Ruth,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like it's special.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.84,0:12:51.82,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,Is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.81,0:12:56.25,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.57,0:13:07.68,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,E-Elias?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.19,0:13:21.24,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.78,0:13:22.88,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.23,0:13:26.66,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,In what way is that book special to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.91,0:13:31.37,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,Er, but we aren't done tidying up the books.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.01,0:13:34.06,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,We can do that whenever.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.92,0:13:41.09,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,I'm your magic teacher, but you're \Nmy human teacher, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.82,0:13:45.81,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's important to answer your \Nstudent's questions as much as you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.51,0:13:48.71,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,I know, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.68,0:13:50.76,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.03,0:13:52.45,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,about that book.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.00,0:13:55.69,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,Please?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.91,0:14:01.43,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.79,0:14:06.99,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Our Slay Vega is telling a story.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.45,0:14:12.69,Default,B,0000,0000,0000,,The beloved child's telling a story?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.07,0:14:15.82,Default,C,0000,0000,0000,,I want to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.88,0:14:25.78,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,I read this book when I was still alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.25,0:14:25.99,sign_20650_157_Voice_of_the_Lon,,0000,0000,0000,,The Lonely Little Star
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.53,0:14:34.19,Magus-flashbackinternal,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,I shouldn't have had you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.44,0:14:36.54,Magus-flashback,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.76,0:14:38.97,Magus-flashback,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.87,0:14:42.31,Magus-flashback,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.78,0:14:50.48,Magus-flashback,A,0000,0000,0000,,She's way too much of a burden to take in.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.48,0:14:53.12,Magus-flashback,A,0000,0000,0000,,And I hear she's odd,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.12,0:14:56.57,Magus-flashback,A,0000,0000,0000,,talking to herself and behaving strangely.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.58,0:15:03.06,Magus-flashback,B,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I heard your mom left you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.06,0:15:06.77,Magus-flashback,C,0000,0000,0000,,No, her mom killed herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.77,0:15:09.51,Magus-flashback,B,0000,0000,0000,,What's the difference? She's an orphan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.51,0:15:11.88,Magus-flashback,B,0000,0000,0000,,She didn't want you, did she?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.00,0:15:18.30,Magus-flashback,A,0000,0000,0000,,Give it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.30,0:15:19.53,Magus-flashback,B,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.01,0:15:21.28,Magus-flashback,A,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.28,0:15:23.49,Magus-flashback,B,0000,0000,0000,,Wait until I'm done.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.49,0:15:24.87,Magus-flashback,A,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.87,0:15:27.17,Magus-flashback,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Please stop making a mess this early.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.93,0:15:27.88,Magus-flashback-overlap,B,0000,0000,0000,,Take it if you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.79,0:15:30.37,Magus-flashback,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.37,0:15:31.65,Magus-flashback,B,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.60,0:15:36.25,Magus-flashback,B,0000,0000,0000,,Time to eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.56,0:15:56.05,Magus-flashback,A,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the food!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.05,0:15:58.13,Magus-flashback,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Put your dishes away first.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.13,0:15:59.74,Magus-flashback,B,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, I'm coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.74,0:16:00.89,Magus-flashback,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.09,0:16:02.84,Magus-flashback,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Daiki, wear your hat,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.84,0:16:03.97,Magus-flashback,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,and take your water bottle!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.05,0:16:15.59,Magus-flashback,A,0000,0000,0000,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.59,0:16:16.78,Magus-flashback,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.53,0:16:27.04,Magus-flashback,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Again?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.29,0:16:29.21,Magus-flashback,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,I'm cleaning it up if you won't eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.92,0:16:34.93,Magus-flashback,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.25,0:16:53.36,Magus-flashback,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Say something, honey.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.36,0:16:56.27,Magus-flashback,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,That girl won't warm up to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.51,0:16:58.83,Magus-flashback,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,She won't even touch the food I made her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.02,0:17:03.83,Magus-flashback,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,What? I gave her the same \Nthing I gave the other two.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.33,0:17:07.36,Magus-flashback,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, what do you mean \Nyou're in the middle of work?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.36,0:17:09.62,Magus-flashback,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,You were the one who \Nsaid you'd take her in!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.00,0:17:13.12,Magus-flashback,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,I really shouldn't have accepted her!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.24,0:18:16.47,Magus-flashback,A,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.64,0:18:20.93,Magus-flashback,A,0000,0000,0000,,Are you hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.19,0:18:22.59,Magus-flashback,A,0000,0000,0000,,One second.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.79,0:18:30.79,Magus-flashback,A,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.65,0:18:33.47,Magus-flashback,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.43,0:18:42.55,Magus-flashback,A,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.55,0:18:45.13,Magus-flashback,B,0000,0000,0000,,What was that for?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.19,0:18:47.86,Magus-flashback,B,0000,0000,0000,,Where are your parents?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.86,0:18:49.60,Magus-flashback,A,0000,0000,0000,,You're bleeding.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.05,0:18:51.31,Magus-flashback,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.92,0:18:55.54,Magus-flashback,A,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.88,0:18:57.03,Magus-flashbackinternal,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.12,0:18:57.96,Magus-flashbackinternal,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.01,0:18:58.93,Magus-flashbackinternal,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.99,0:18:59.99,Magus-flashbackinternal,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.03,0:19:00.70,Magus-flashbackinternal,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.21,0:20:08.55,Magus-flashback,A,0000,0000,0000,,Is someone there?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.83,0:20:13.97,Magus-flashback,A,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.98,0:20:17.85,Magus-flashback,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.85,0:20:19.25,Magus-flashback,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,I'll leave immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.30,0:20:54.32,Magus-flashback,A,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.45,0:20:57.37,Magus-flashback,A,0000,0000,0000,,Those creepy things can't come in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.95,0:21:00.25,Magus-flashback,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,You can see them?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.71,0:21:04.03,Magus-flashback,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you, Onii-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.35,0:21:06.93,Magus-flashback,A,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the magician of the forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.34,0:21:10.41,Magus-flashback,A,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.57,0:21:15.14,Magus-flashback,A,0000,0000,0000,,To the library of the forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.67,0:22:48.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.13,0:22:54.80,Magus-internal/narrator,A,0000,0000,0000,,The young man stood amidst \Nthe huge collection of books.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.60,0:22:59.51,Magus-internal/narrator,A,0000,0000,0000,,What does the girl dream of in her nap?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.51,0:23:02.99,Magus-internal/narrator,A,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I should just take her away.
